name: Self Discovered
description:
"Some things' in life seem a little strange at first, but paycheck is paycheck..." Self Discovered

is a backrooms-inspired indie horror game where atmosphere is key. You play as a lost team member of an underground cleaning company, needing to roam the dreaded halls of your new work place.
